(ns farsund.window.events
  (:require [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [taoensso.encore :as e]
            [taoensso.encore :as e]))



(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/update-window-size
  (fn [{db :db} [_ {:keys [inner-height inner-width client-height]}]]
    {:db         (update db :window assoc
                         :inner-height inner-height
                         :inner-width inner-width
                         :client-height client-height)
     :dispatch-n [[:window/update-breakpoint]
                  [:layout/update-gutter]]}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/update-scroll
  (fn [{db :db} [_ {:keys [scroll-top scroll-height]}]]
    (let [previous-top (get-in db [:window :scroll-top])
          scroll-down? (> scroll-top previous-top)
          old-timeout (get-in db [:window :scrolling-timeout])
          scrolling-timeout (e/after-timeout 166
                                             (rf/dispatch [:do
                                                           [:turn-off [[:window :scrolling?]]]
                                                           [:clean-up [[:window :scrolling-timeout]]]]))]
      (when old-timeout
        (e/tf-cancel! old-timeout))
      (when (not= scroll-top previous-top)
        {:db (update db :window assoc
                     :scrolling? true
                     :scrolling-timeout scrolling-timeout
                     :scroll-top scroll-top
                     :scroll-height scroll-height
                     :scrolling-down scroll-down?
                     :scrolling-up (not scroll-down?))}))))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/scroll-smooth-pos
  (fn [_ [_ pos]]
    {:window/scroll-smooth pos}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/scroll-to-second-header
  (fn [_ _]
    {:window/scroll-smooth 180}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/scroll-to-top
  (fn [_ _]
    {:window/scroll-smooth 0}))


(rf/reg-event-db
  :window/update-breakpoint
  (fn [db _]
    (let [width (get-in db [:window :inner-width])
          breakpoint (cond
                       (< width 600) :xs
                       (and (>= width 600) (< width 960)) :sm
                       (and (>= width 960) (< width 1280)) :md
                       (and (>= width 1280) (< width 1920)) :lg
                       (>= width 1920) :xl)]
      (assoc-in db [:window :breakpoint] breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-event-db
  :layout/update-gutter
  (fn [db _]
    (let [width (get-in db [:window :inner-width])
          gutter (cond
                   (< width 600) 16
                   (>= width 600) 24)]
      (assoc-in db [:layout :gutter] gutter))))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/add-on-scroll-listener
  (fn [_ [_ coll]]
    {:window/on-scroll coll}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/remove-on-scroll-listener
  (fn [_ [_ config]]
    {:window/stop-on-scroll config}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/add-on-resize-listener
  (fn [_ [_ coll]]
    {:window/on-resize coll}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/remove-on-resize-listener
  (fn [_ [_ config]]
    {:window/stop-on-resize config}))



(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/run-resize-listener!
  (fn [_ _]
    {:window/on-resize   [{:dispatch    [:window/update-window-size]
                           :debounce-ms 32
                           :id          :window/on-resize}]
     :window/init-window [[:window/update-window-size]
                          [:window/update-scroll]]}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :window/run-scroll-listener!
  (fn [_ _]
    {:window/on-scroll [{:dispatch    [:window/update-scroll]
                         :debounce-ms 32
                         :id          :window/on-scroll}]}))
